SEQUENCE:9
DESCRIPTION;LANGUAGE=en-US:Dear all\,\n\nWe have the pleasure of inviting y
 ou to our CPDSE Episode Meetings.\n\nWe will have these meetings every six
  weeks as a physical meeting alternating between SDU and KU. The meetings 
 at KU will be at CPDSE\, Jagtvej 160\, 1st floor and at SDU you can use th
 is map<https://clients.mapsindoors.com/sdu/573f26e4bc1f571b08094312/search
 > to guide you to the meeting room.\n\nOur default agenda is:\n\n  *   Cir
 cle Sync: Individual circles meet internally to review their progress on t
 he Episode's goal. The output is a clear status update to share with the l
 arger group. Commitments are captured directly as Todo-items and decisions
  are documented as Messages.\n  *   Break / Lunch 🥪\n  *   Center Sync:
  All circles come together to share their progress. Each circle presents a
  brief\, high-level summary of their work\, highlighting key accomplishmen
 ts and any dependencies or blockers.\n  *   Pharma Data Science Showcase: 
 Research Circle organizes scientific talks and workshops (Storebælt serie
 s).\n\nWe will be serving lunch at the meeting\, so we kindly ask that you
  reply to the invitation\, so we know how many people to expect. If you ha
 ve any dietary restrictions/allergies\, please let Jeppe know.\n\nLooking 
 forward to seeing you.\n\nBest\,\nMorten & Jeppe\n\nJeppe Hartmann\nProjec
 t Coordinator\n\nUniversity of Copenhagen\nDepartment of Drug Design and P
 harmacology\n\nUniversitetsparken 2\nDK - 2100 Copenhagen\nDenmark\nLync/S
 kype +45 35323413\njeppe.hartmann@sund.ku.dk<mailto:jeppe.hartmann@sund.ku
 .dk>\n\n[Logo for Københavns Universitet]\n\nHow we protect personal data
 <https://informationssikkerhed.ku.dk/english/protection-of-information-pri
 vacy/privacy-policy/>\n\n\n
SUMMARY;LANGUAGE=en-US:CPDSE Episode Meeting
LOCATION;LANGUAGE=en-US:KU\, Jagtvej 160\, 1st floor\, CPDSE meeting room
STATUS:CONFIRMED
ATTENDEE;ROLE=OPT-PARTICIPANT;RSVP=TRUE;CN=calendar@cpdse.dk;X-PM-TOKEN=59e
 1e823e5b8c5ec3a958f8a54e4df7b2f6b9587;PARTSTAT=NEEDS-ACTION:mailto:calenda
 r@cpdse.dk
END:VEVENT
